Class ReportBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.axelor.db.Model
      • com.axelor.auth.db.AuditableModel
        • com.axelor.studio.db.ReportBuilder

  • @Entity
public class ReportBuilder
extends com.axelor.auth.db.AuditableModel
    This class use to generate template from selected view and also add button in view. It will store template and header/footer in html format. It will be used to generate html report for a record.
